     Winter Olympics Preparedness
   In the weeks following the September 11 attack on the United States,
   questions have naturally arisen about the role of the Federal Emergency
   Management Agency (FEMA) at the 2002 Olympic Games in Utah. The links
   below lead to information that should help answer those questions.
   FEMA Region VIII Olympic Links
